@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.52 * 0.83)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.52)) * wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.04)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v0 + 0.86) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.45)))
    v1 = 0.87
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.06)) / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.88) + (v1 + 0.42 / v0 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
